{"tid":1667006,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[民賤聯你仲駛選?]毛漢透露鄭泳舜叫他說話要小心點　鄭泳舜：無其他用意","createTime":"2019-10-21T08:27:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T08:37:40.000Z","uid":51271,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4b3ae0e6684d5d9b57ca7f0346f041651e3a873a","tid":1667006,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T08:27:37.000Z","msg":"印度協會前主席毛漢(Mohan Chugani)說，昨日下午身處九龍清真寺外，被警方水炮車藍色水劑射中，感覺全身像著火，之後到醫院治理。他認為警方應就水炮車射中清真寺事件道歉，又形容香港現時像「無王法」。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">毛漢又透露，民建聯立法會議員鄭泳舜昨晚到他家探望，並叫他與傳媒說話時要小心一點，不要被人利用。但毛漢說，會直接講出事件。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n鄭泳舜書面回覆查詢說，昨日知悉情況後聯同黨友前往探望，慰問傷勢及了解可提供甚麼協助。鄭泳舜說，探望期間雙方亦有討論香港近日事件，希望各方以及少數族裔一同攜手化解現時社會分裂，讓香港重回正軌，並無其他用意。<br />\n<br />\n他又說，昨晚將毛漢的意見，即時向保安局及警方轉達，並於今早聯絡政務司司長辦公室，要求當局即時正視清真寺事件，盡快落區向少數族裔宗教團體解釋。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1487434-20191021.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1487434-20191021.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=bp2T%2F%2B5c5q8hcpZmRI3qNp6X7PLg0GRX82CuX%2BG2FI0%3D&h=afdafda8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1487434-20191021.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=55bdc9fa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1487434-20191021.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"66dcc548209fb1c5e9b901c44393ecf344ec8658","tid":1667006,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T08:27:46.000Z","msg":"不如全港黨鐵靜坐聲討721啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1665580\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1665580</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87573286c3e007bc1d86331e4c77c3d597c1c281","tid":1667006,"uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyT